OL,3,CClimbing on Holocaust Memorial Garden
OL,4,Cto become a crime ` Lords
OL,6,FClimbing over Hyde Park's Holocaust
OL,7,FMemorial Garden is set to become a
OL,8,Fcrime, after a monument was covered up
OL,9,Fwhile a demonstration took place
OL,10,Fnearby.
OL,12,FPeers agreed to add the London garden,
OL,13,Fcomprising boulders and birch trees,
OL,14,Fto a draft list of memorials where
OL,15,Fministers have proposed a ban on
OL,16,Fclimbing, as part of the Crime and
OL,17,FPolicing Bill.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
