PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773230584
OL,3,CClimbing on Holocaust Memorial Garden
OL,4,Cto become a crime ` Lords
OL,6,FPeople who clamber over the garden
OL,7,Fwithout "a good reason" would face up
OL,8,Fto three months in prison and a fine
OL,9,Fof up to #1,000.
OL,11,FIt will be listed alongside the The
OL,12,FCenotaph in Whitehall, Birmingham's
OL,13,FHall of Memory, the Liverpool
OL,14,FCenotaph, The Response in Newcastle
OL,15,Fand the Portsmouth Naval War Memorial.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
