CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773230584
OL,3,CClimbing on Holocaust Memorial Garden
OL,4,Cto become a crime ` Lords
OL,6,FThey included the Monument to the
OL,7,FWomen of World War II in Whitehall,
OL,8,Funveiled on the 60th anniversary of
OL,9,Fthe end of the war in 2005, which
OL,10,Fpeers also agreed to add to the list
OL,11,Fon Monday.
OL,13,FLord Katz, speaking for the
OL,14,FGovernment, said both monuments were
OL,15,F"culturally significant" and indicated
OL,16,Fministers supported Lord Parkinson's
OL,17,Fproposal.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
