OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773230584
OL,3,CClimbing on Holocaust Memorial Garden
OL,4,Cto become a crime ` Lords
OL,6,FHe added: "The Holocaust Memorial
OL,7,FGarden in Hyde Park is, of course,
OL,8,Fdesigned to be enjoyed as a garden and
OL,9,Fpeople are free to walk within it.
OL,11,F"I've given consideration to the
OL,12,Fpractical issue of whether the police
OL,13,Fwill be able to enforce this offence.
OL,15,F"The intention of the offence is to
OL,16,Fcapture the act of climbing and I'm
OL,17,Fconfident it will not capture walking
OL,18,Fon an installation such as the
OL,19,FHolocaust Memorial Garden.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773230584
OL,3,CClimbing on Holocaust Memorial Garden
OL,4,Cto become a crime ` Lords
OL,6,F"Further, there are, of course, other
OL,7,Fmemorials listed in (the Bill) which
OL,8,Fhave steps which may be sat on by
OL,9,Fmembers of the public, such as the
OL,10,FRoyal Artillery Memorial in Hyde Park.
OL,12,F"I am content that in enforcing this
OL,13,Foffence, police officers will use
OL,14,Ftheir discretion to consider whether
OL,15,Fan offence is committed."
OL,17,FLord Katz said the Bill "intentionally
OL,18,Fsets out a clear and fixed list of
OL,19,Fmemorials, which provides certainty
OL,20,Ffor the public, policing and the
OL,21,Fcourts".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@YO]yD@YOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
