OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773230584
OL,3,CClimbing on Holocaust Memorial Garden
OL,4,Cto become a crime ` Lords
OL,6,FHe warned that including any listed or
OL,7,Fscheduled memorial risked "undermining
OL,8,Fthe clarity and consistency that the
OL,9,Fmeasure is intended to achieve".
OL,11,FThe Government has also amended its
OL,12,FBill to ban protests outside homes
OL,13,Fwhere public office-holders, including
OL,14,FMPs, peers, members of the Senedd and
OL,15,Fthe mayor of London, live.
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773230584
OL,3,CClimbing on Holocaust Memorial Garden
OL,4,Cto become a crime ` Lords
OL,6,FSeveral properties are exempt from the
OL,7,Fban, including 10, 11 and 12 Downing
OL,8,FStreet, the Palace of Westminster, the
OL,9,FPrime Minister's country retreat
OL,10,FChequers in Buckinghamshire, and the
OL,11,FForeign Secretary's country retreat at
OL,12,FChevening House, Kent.
OL,14,FLord Katz said "harassment and
OL,15,Fintimidation must never be accepted as
OL,16,Fa part of a public office-holder's
OL,17,Frole".
OL,26,@vD@POUyD@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
