OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773230584
OL,3,CClimbing on Holocaust Memorial Garden
OL,4,Cto become a crime ` Lords
OL,6,FHe also said: "It is perfectly
OL,7,Flegitimate for campaigners during
OL,8,Felection time to doorknock and to
OL,9,Fspeak to their local public office-
OL,10,Fholders about a different political
OL,11,Fopinion.
OL,13,F"Where this crosses the line is when
OL,14,Fthese people choose to protest against
OL,15,Fthe public office-holder at their
OL,16,Fhome."
OL,18,FThe Bill faces further scrutiny before
OL,19,Fit can become law.
OL,26,@nD@OOUuD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/10
